<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Prüfer-Verwaltung | THW LAZ</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; padding: 30px; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        h1 { color: #003399; margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; }
        th { text-align: left; padding: 12px; background: #f8f9fa; color: #666; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
        td { padding: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; vertical-align: middle; }
        
        .input-edit { 
            padding: 8px 12px; 
            border: 1px solid #ddd; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            width: 180px; 
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            outline: none;
        }
        .input-edit:focus { border-color: #003399; box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(0,51,153,0.1); }

        .btn { padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; font-size: 0.85rem; }
        .btn-green { background: #2ecc71; color: white; }
        .btn-blue { background: #003399; color: white; }
        .btn-save { background: #f0f4ff; color: #003399; border: 1px solid #003399; }
        .btn-save:hover { background: #003399; color: white; }
        
        .link-pill { background: #f1f5f9; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 6px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #64748b; }
        
        .station-label { font-weight: 800; color: #1e293b; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
            <h1><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> Prüfer-Accounts verwalten</h1>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                <a href="/admin/export-pruefer" class="btn btn-green"><i class="fas fa-file-csv"></i> CSV Export</a>
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-blue">Zurück</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">Hier kannst du die Anzeigenamen und Passwörter der Stationen ändern. Der Login erfolgt über die Station (z.B. "1") und das Passwort.</p>

        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Station</th>
                    <th>Anzeigename (auf iPad)</th>
                    <th>Passwort</th>
                    <th>Link (QR-Ziel)</th>
                    <th>Aktion</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
<tbody>
    <% accounts.forEach(a => { %>
    <tr>
        <form action="/admin/update-pruefer" method="POST" id="form-<%= a.station %>">
            <input type="hidden" name="station" value="<%= a.station %>">
            
            <td class="station-label">
                <i class="fas fa-desktop" style="color: #cbd5e1; margin-right: 5px;"></i> 
                <%= a.station %>
            </td>
            
            <td>
                <input type="text" name="anzeigename" value="<%= a.anzeigename %>" class="input-edit">
            </td>
            
            <td>
                <input type="text" name="passwort" value="<%= a.passwort %>" class="input-edit">
            </td>
            
            <td>
                <span class="link-pill">/station/<%= a.station %></span>
            </td>
            
            <td>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px;">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-save">
                        <i class="fas fa-save"></i>
                    </button>

                    <a href="/admin/delete-pruefer/<%= a.station %>" 
                       class="btn" 
                       style="background: #fee2e2; color: #ef4444; border: 1px solid #fecaca;"
                       onclick="return confirm('Möchtest du den Prüfer für Station <%= a.station %> wirklich löschen?')">
                        <i class="fas fa-trash-alt"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </td>
        </form>
    </tr>
    <% }) %>
</tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>
</html>